    "title": "😀😄😂😭 Awesome Sentiment Analysis 😥😟😱😤  [![Awesome](https://cdn.rawgit.com/sindresorhus/awesome/d7305f38d29fed78fa85652e3a63e154dd8e8829/media/badge.svg)](https://github.com/sindresorhus/awesome)",
